*Koji* muškarac je učinio to? (Which man did it?)

*Kojem* danu treba da se vratim? (Which day should I return?)

*Kojemu* je datumu potpisan sporazum? (Which date was the agreement signed?)

*Kojima* bojama je ova slika? (What colors is this painting?)

*Kojemu* piscu se moja mama najviše divi? (Which writer does my mother admire the most?)

*Kojim* instrumentima sviraju u ovoj bini? (Which instruments are played on this stage?)

*Kojima* se sredstvima pridobijanje klijenata? (Which means are used for obtaining clients?)

*Kojemu* se čoveku može verovati? (Which man can you trust?)